name: Army Jungle Warfare - Sniper Shooter Assassin Strike Force Edition
name_original: Army Jungle Warfare - Sniper Shooter Assassin Strike Force Edition
description:
** SNIPER KILLS, HEADSHOTS, & MORE! **
** ACTION PACKED SNIPER SHOOTING GAME! **

You are the "best of the best" on a mission to take out a rouge agent. Armed with your sniper rifle, you are given the dangerous mission to eliminate the target.

FEATURES

- Headshots, sniper kills, and more!
- Multiple levels.
- Non stop action!

Are you up for the challenge?
